{"tid":499518,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓記者遭15強國警衞毆傷 南韓頭版報道記協譴責","createTime":"2017-12-15T02:06:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T06:33:49.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4532ab95619ea4c102eb6a0cef0f91e276d46623","tid":499518,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T02:06:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171215/large/1513302081_3489.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171215%2Flarge%2F1513302081_3489.jpg&h=d8ab1adc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南韓總統文在寅正在中國訪問，意味兩國關係回暖，但南韓2名記者昨日在北京採訪期間，遭中方15名警衞毆打。南韓記者協會昨日發表聲明譴責，並向中國政府表示抗議。<br />\n<br />\n韓聯社報道，南韓記者協會在聲明中表示，中方毆打韓方記者是無法容忍的行為。這不僅鎮壓新聞自由，更是一種侮辱。《東亞日報》今日則以頭版顯著報道事件，外界已認為文在寅此行受到中國外交單位冷落，如今又發生記者被打的暴力事件，分析指出，兩國之間的矛盾關係短期內難以化解。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171215/57583589\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171215%2F57583589&d=b%2B13yFKnwMUrPr%2BsLJSIFaMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=fba1e227\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171215%2F57583589&h=4d69950a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171215/57583589</a>"},{"pid":"3faa9e8528dfd358ed58ef5ce633c57048e6239a","tid":499518,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T02:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b6a9a1d75a72f908b5824e6cba5fd30f952bc0d","tid":499518,"uid":10890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T02:27:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/15/102707_ce69e34205a6860dd09f20d1a4a5cf8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-h